OL,5, Millions of people are borrowing to pay
OL,6, essential bills at Christmas, charities
OL,7, warn, with energy debts a key concern  
OL,8, as prices are set to rise again.       
OL,10,FCitizens Advice said it was seeing more
OL,11,Fpeople falling behind on energy bills  
OL,12,Fas winter began, owing an average of   
OL,13,F#1,841 to their supplier.              
OL,15,FThe government said its cost-of-living 
OL,16,Fpayments were easing the burden.       
OL,18,FCharities say some families face paying
OL,19,Foff loans, adding to the financial     
OL,20,Fstrain as they cut back on basics.     
